data.description:
Featuring one of the largest floor plans in the neighborhood; upon entering this home walkthrough a flex room to the right. Continuing onto an open concept kitchen, with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, large island, and well sized pantry overlooking one of two living rooms! Downstairs features an additional bedroom along with a full bathroom. Upstairs has a large primary bedroom with a primary bathroom offering double sinks and walk in closet! An additional living room is upstairs along with three more additional bedrooms, another full bathroom, and a large laundry room! Plenty of storage throughout home makes this home very functional! With a fenced backyard and 2 car garage the home is complete. 
HOA amenities include community pool, dog park, playground, & clubhouse with kitchen/BBQ area.
Buyer to verify all info.
